data.description: Welcome to this adorable Cape Cod in Westville NJ.  This home offers you 3 beds and 1 bath and a big basement with walk-up access to the back of the home. This lot has a side yard with one 2 car parking gravel driveway.  As you enter the front door, you will encounter the living room freshly painted with laminated hardwood flooring and recessed lightning.  Moving through you have the dining room with the kitchen off to the left.  The kitchen has a gas cooking stove with dishwasher, microwave and refrigerator and a door to access the deck on the side of the home. The full bath is on the opposite side of the dining room with a tub shower/combo, two bedrooms with standard closets finish the main floor.  The upper level has 1 bedroom on either side of the stairs with original hardwood flooring (can be used as two beds).  The basement is unfinished with washer and dryer, new hot water heater, high ceilings and walk up with dormer doors.  The side yard provides you with some lawn area with a shed and deck off of the house. Make your appointment for tour today!
